{"messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Hello, Mizzenmast! That's a great name—it has a nautical ring to it (literally, since a mizzenmast is the rearmost mast on a ship). Nice to meet you! \n\nIs there anything I can help you with today?"}]},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"If you had one, what would be your favorite color? (Please don't mention my name.)"}]}],"model":"claude-haiku-4-5"}